---
title: Lemongrass Beef Stir-Fry
description: Lemongrass is the key ingredient in this simple stir-fry - its mellow, lemony flavor imparts authentic Vietnamese flavor into the dish. Be sure to only mince the innermost core - the outer layers can be very tough!
